# 🌱 Youth Mental Wellness AI

A Generative AI-powered youth mental wellness app with:

- 💬 **AI Chat Support** (empathetic conversations)
- 😊 **Daily Mood Check-In** (track emotions)
- 📘 **Resource Suggestions** (self-care tips + helpline links)

---

## 🚀 Features (Prototype)
1. Type a message → get an **empathetic AI response**  
2. Select your **daily mood emoji/scale**  
3. Receive **personalized self-care suggestions**  

---

## 🌐 Live Demo
👉 [Try the app here](https://huggingface.co/spaces/vigneshyadala/youth-mental-wellness-ai)

---

## 📌 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** Streamlit
- **Backend (Prototype):** Python
- **Deployment:** Hugging Face Spaces

